cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper focuses on computer vision techniques for autonomous vehicles, specifically adapting deep network architectures for 360{\deg} panoramic imagery. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) categories. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper evaluates its approach using an automotive environment simulator, which could fall under the graphics (cs.GR) category.
